title: Digantara raises $50 million to expand from space surveillance to missile defense
description:
Digantara Industries, an Indian space situational awareness company, has raised $50 million as it expands into the United States and pursues opportunities in missile defense.

The post Digantara raises $50 million to expand from space surveillance to missile defense appeared first on SpaceNews.
